### Sample CRUD App API Tests
@host = http://localhost:8000

# ============================================================
# Basic CRUD
# ============================================================

### 1. Create a user  →  DB_QUERY + MQ_PRODUCE
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

###

### 2. Create another user
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane@example.com"
}

###

### 3. Get all users  →  DB_QUERY
GET {{host}}/users

###

### 4. Get user by ID  →  DB_QUERY
GET {{host}}/users/1

###

### 5. Update user  →  DB_QUERY + CACHE_DEL + MQ_PRODUCE
PUT {{host}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com"
}

###

### 6. Delete user  →  DB_QUERY + CACHE_DEL + MQ_PRODUCE
DELETE {{host}}/users/2

# ============================================================
# Cache (Redis)
# ============================================================

### 7. Cache MISS then HIT  →  CACHE_MISS + DB_QUERY + CACHE_SET / CACHE_HIT
# Run twice: first call = MISS (DB lookup + cache write), second = HIT (cache only)
GET {{host}}/users/cache/1

# ============================================================
# Kafka
# ============================================================

### 8. Send Kafka message  →  MQ_PRODUCE + MQ_CONSUME (async)
POST {{host}}/users/message?msg=HelloTracing

# ============================================================
# HTTP out (RestTemplate)
# ============================================================

### 9. External HTTP call (self)  →  HTTP_OUT OK
GET {{host}}/users/external

### 10. Trigger outbound HTTP error  →  HTTP_OUT ERR (errorType + errorMessage)
GET {{host}}/users/trigger-http-error

# ============================================================
# Trace scenario samples
# ============================================================

### 11. Full chain  →  HTTP_IN + DB_QUERY × 2 + CACHE_SET × N + MQ_PRODUCE + HTTP_OUT
GET {{host}}/users/chain

###

### 12. Bulk insert (10 records)  →  DB_QUERY × 10 연속 span
POST {{host}}/users/bulk?count=10

###

### 13. Bulk insert (50 records)  →  더 많은 DB span 확인
POST {{host}}/users/bulk?count=50

###

### 14. Error simulation: 500  →  HTTP_IN ERR (응답은 정상 전달됨)
GET {{host}}/users/error?code=500

###

### 15. Error simulation: 404  →  HTTP_IN ERR
GET {{host}}/users/error?code=404

### 16. Error
GET {{host}}/error
